name: Shim Sham
description: Shim Sham: an electric neon pink that glows in the dark! It is filled with silver holo glitter.

name: The Style Collection
description:
Includes:
*It Girl
*Faboo
*Obvi
*Glam

name: Glam
description: Glam is a shimmery light green base with green and silver holo, with green, pink, and white squares, white hexes. Its amazing.

name: Obvi
description: Obvi is a mint green base with blue and green holo, with silver, blue, red, purple, black, and yellow hexes, silver moons and stars, blue glitter strands, black glitter shatters. Its loaded!!!

name: Faboo
description: Faboo is a purple based polish with blue, silver, and green holo glitter, and white strand glitter, white & black hexes, dark green, light green and blue squares!! Beautiful!

name: It Girl
description: A lovely light pink base with so much glitter; Blue stars, sliver large hexes, purple & pink medium hexes, itty bitty black & pink hexes, silver circles, and white squares!

name: Change Me
description:
A reddish brown base with brown glitter. Very light sensitive. It looks different in various light settings.

Below is show 2 coats with no undies. 
Top half is in artificial light, bottom left is direct sunlight, and bottom right is outdoors in the shade.

name: Whispering Winds
description:
A clear base with green, blue, white, and silver glitters of all shapes.

Picture shown is 2 coats over black.

name: Old School
description:
A clear base with black and white glitter strands, circles, and squares of all sizes.

This picture is one coat over 2 coats of tart heart.
(don't forget to pick up a bottle of tart heart to complete this look)

name: Bottom Of the Barrel
description:
Some times when i sell out of a discontinued polish, I will still have a little left; just not enough for a full 15ml bottle. SO when this happens I am left with "bottom of the barrel" polish. 
I don't want to throw away good polish, so I put it in 5ml bottles and sell it for a cheaper price.
 
New polishes are being added to this section so check back often!

name: In Luck
description: In luck is a salty see green base mixed in with green and silver holo specs and slightly larger silver hexs. The pictures show 2 coats with no base. Like this polish? Why not get a matching Cabochon Ring!

description:
Support your school!

name: Fall Forward- The Fall Collection
description:
This is the entire fall collection. 
*Burning Bridges

Aside from being the fall collection it also has another theme. Try not to dwell on the past, it's behind you. Look forward to the change that the winds are bringing as the seasons change.

Does not contain DBP, Toluene, or formaldehyde. To keep your nails happy!
5ml
